Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount default
  Host imap.fastmail.com
  PassCmd "netrc-password imap.fastmail.com mail'@'danil.mobi"
  SSLType IMAPS
  User "mail"@"danil.mobi"

IMAPStore remote
  Account default

MaildirStore local
  Inbox ~/mail/Inbox
  Path ~/mail/

Channel default
  Master :remote:
  Pattern % !Notes !Trash
  Slave :local:
